      'FIX D ÔÇö BRAKING EVENT LOGIC: Entry stays at 1.5 m/s┬▓. Hysteresis at 1.2 m/s┬▓. Acceptance: sampleCount >= 2 AND deltaKmh >= 3.0. Rich metadata: deltaKmh, sampleCount, highSpeedStart, intensity.',
